Subject:    <a href="?t=95837890700028&r=1&w=2">Re: Domain name or host name?</a>
From:       <a href="?a=95837785200016&r=1&w=2">aramis.rutgers.edu!athos.rutgers.edu!hedrick () rutgers ! edu  (Charles Hedrick)</a>
